&lt;li&gt;Office Visits &amp;amp; Meetings: Help coordinate office visits and in-person meetings with internal teams and external partners as necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend artist shows after work hours as necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
