&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Partnership Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the strategic relationship with the assigned DSP(s), serving as the primary commercial and strategic contact for key counterparts. You will cultivate a collaborative culture, align team goals, and foster cross-functional collaboration to advance business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Ownership &amp;amp; Modeling:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the financial health of the assigned account. Partner closely with the Corporate Strategy team to build and maintain sophisticated financial reports that track revenue performance against targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Influence &amp;amp; Strategic Presence:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and maintain deep-seated relationships at the assigned DSP through consistent face-to-face engagement. You will act as a trusted in-person partner and networker at partner and label offices. You will leverage this extensive physical presence to secure competitive advantage, open doors for premium opportunities, and foster the impactful industry connections necessary to advance territory goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weekly Performance Reporting:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the development and delivery of weekly streaming reports that assess the health of the account. You will clearly communicate the impact of team initiatives week-over-week, identifying specific drivers of growth or decline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure optimal alignment across all assigned account stakeholders (ie: Partnerships, Editorial, Marketing) for revenue-driving releases. You will act as the centralized leader for execution while coaching and mentoring junior team members to ensure high-level results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with Relationship Leads and label clients to integrate best practices into high-value pitches. You will implement solutions that align with business goals as a strategic problem solver, facilitating comprehensive solutions through collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
