&lt;p&gt;Located in our Chile office, this position will be hyper-focused on supporting our Latin labels and artists and will be responsible for developing and executing paid media campaigns across LATAM. This position reports directly to The Orchard Chile’s Country Manager, and receives functional guidance from the Senior Director of Global Paid Media &amp;amp; Growth Strategy in the NYC office.&lt;/p&gt;
